    <briefdescription>
<para><bold>foldl_matrix</bold>(Pred, A, V0, VF) </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Apply Pred(A,Index,V1,V2) to every element of matrix <emphasis>A</emphasis>, where <emphasis>Index</emphasis> ranges over all entries in the array</para>
<para>As an example, to sum all elements of a numeric matrix: <programlisting filename=".prolog"><codeline><highlight class="stringliteral"></highlight><highlight class="normal">add(</highlight><highlight class="charliteral">A</highlight><highlight class="normal">,<sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="charliteral">I</highlight><highlight class="normal">,<sp/></highlight><highlight class="charliteral">S0</highlight><highlight class="normal">,<sp/></highlight><highlight class="charliteral">S</highlight><highlight class="normal">)<sp/></highlight><highlight class="keyword">:-</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/></highlight><highlight class="stringliteral"></highlight><highlight class="normal">matrix_get(<sp/></highlight><highlight class="charliteral">A</highlight><highlight class="normal">,<sp/></highlight><highlight class="charliteral">I</highlight><highlight class="normal">,<sp/></highlight><highlight class="charliteral">V</highlight><highlight class="normal">),<sp/></highlight><highlight class="charliteral">S</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/></highlight><highlight class="keyword">is</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/></highlight><highlight class="charliteral">S0</highlight><highlight class="keyword">+</highlight><highlight class="charliteral">V</highlight><highlight class="normal">.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="stringliteral"></highlight><highlight class="normal">sum_matrix(</highlight><highlight class="charliteral">A</highlight><highlight class="normal">,</highlight><highlight class="charliteral">S</highlight><highlight class="normal">)<sp/></highlight><highlight class="keyword">:-</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/></highlight><highlight class="stringliteral"></highlight><highlight class="normal">foldl_matrix(add,</highlight><highlight class="charliteral">A</highlight><highlight class="normal">,</highlight><highlight class="vhldigit">0</highlight><highlight class="normal">,</highlight><highlight class="charliteral">S</highlight><highlight class="normal">).</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
